# AI Agent Rules - Receipt Extractor

## Circular Exchange Framework (Mandatory)

All code MUST integrate with the Circular Exchange Framework.

### Required Pattern

```python
# At top of every Python file:
try:
    from shared.circular_exchange import PROJECT_CONFIG, ModuleRegistration, PackageRegistry
    CIRCULAR_EXCHANGE_AVAILABLE = True
except ImportError:
    CIRCULAR_EXCHANGE_AVAILABLE = False

# After imports:
if CIRCULAR_EXCHANGE_AVAILABLE:
    try:
        PROJECT_CONFIG.register_module(ModuleRegistration(
            module_id="your.module.id",
            file_path=__file__,
            description="Description",
            dependencies=["deps"],
            exports=["exports"]
        ))
    except Exception:
        pass

# Use VariablePackage for configuration
_registry = PackageRegistry() if CIRCULAR_EXCHANGE_AVAILABLE else None
```

### Reference: shared/models/ocr_config.py
